      Policy paper
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    The UK's points-based immigration system: policy statement
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This policy statement sets out the government's plans for a new UK points-based immigration system.</p>

  </div>
</div>

