<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This policy statement includes information on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the scope of the points-based system</li>
  <li>salary and skills thresholds for skilled workers</li>
  <li>a route for highly-skilled workers</li>
  <li>reducing the overall number of lower-skilled workers</li>
  <li>the visa process</li>
  <li>crossing the UK border</li>
  <li>engagement and outreach</li>
  <li>Migration Advisory Committee analysis of a points-based system</li>
</ul>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/new-immigration-system-what-you-need-to-know" class="govuk-link">Sign up for email alerts to get updates on the new immigration system</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>

